props.children:
## Kubectl Dashboard
In this notebook, Kui offers 4 watchers to monitor your namespaces, deployments, pods and events.

In each watcher, you can further inspect resources via clicking. The resource details will be presented in the lower right terminal.

#### Craft your own dashboard!

You can craft your own dashboard by adding your favorite watch commands, like `kubectl top nodes` and `kubectl krew` commands, and customize your watch experience.
